    <section anchor="UDPOPT-CCO" title="Checksum Compensation Option">
        <t>
       The CCO is added to the option space to allow for devices incorrectly 
       calculating the udp checksum. The CCO has the following format.
        </t>
            <figure anchor="fig-echores" title="UDP ECHORES Option Format">
                <artwork align="center"><![CDATA[
        +---------+--------+------------+
        | Kind=xx | Len=4  |  Checksum  |
        +---------+--------+------------+
          1 byte    1 byte    2 bytes       
                ]]></artwork>
            </figure>
    </section>

